  3.575611857357772*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1b4fc725-74f9-404f-8228-\
72be13130c43"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "A nuclide may be referenced either by its mass number, or by a text string \
of the form ",
 StyleBox["\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]23Na\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ". If the mass number is ambiguous, a warning is generated, and the text \
string form must be used."
}], "Text",
